		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.chenky.com/archives/228" rel="bookmark">数据库杂谈之：如何优雅的进行表结构设计</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">发表于</span><a href="http://www.chenky.com/archives/228" title="下午4:30" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2016-05-21T16:30:39+00:00">2016年5月21日</time></a><span class="by-author"><span class="sep">由</span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.chenky.com/archives/author/admin" title="查看所有由陈恺垣发布的文章" rel="author">陈恺垣</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.chenky.com/archives/228#respond"><span class="leave-reply">回复</span></a>			</div>
